An independent approach
							



















About Us









Troy Asset Management is an independent fund management company founded in 2000. Our investment style is unconventional, yet conservative.

 







 

Troy was founded to focus on absolute rather than relative returns, and aims to preserve and grow its investors’ capital over the very long-term. Over the years we have attracted other investors who share this patient attitude to investment management, including family offices, wealth managers, investment advisers, charities and endowments. 
Our aim is to keep investors’ costs down by maintaining a competitive fee structure and keeping portfolio turnover to a minimum. We do not charge performance fees – believing that we are rewarded by the loyalty of our investors.
For more information please see The Funds.

 













 

